txt.en: You have entered a forest overwhelmed with spiders in Cirith Ungol.\n\nYou should defeat many spiders in Taurlingol.
'You know what you have to do, [placeholder]. The only good spider is a dead spider, and since I'm injured, I leave it to you! Go into that accursed forest and kill the spiders!'
Atli knows there is only one solution when you enter a spider-infested forest.
'So, how many did you kill? 15? Eh, not bad. I suspect you'll add to that count before you're finished in Cirith Ungol!'
Atli can be found on a hill near Taurlingol.\n\nYou should talk to Atli Spider-bane.
